that the defendant
be sentenced to 25 years in prison.

933
00:59:07,878 --> 00:59:10,714
Defense, present your closing statement.

934
00:59:18,680 --> 00:59:19,931
Your Honor,

935
00:59:20,557 --> 00:59:23,894
I speak today not only
as the defense attorney

936
00:59:23,977 --> 00:59:26,146
but also as an individual

937
00:59:26,229 --> 00:59:29,191
who sincerely acknowledges
the gravity of this matter.

938
00:59:29,274 --> 00:59:30,650
The defendant, Kim Yeong-mi,

939
00:59:30,734 --> 00:59:34,237
was a victim
of severe school bullying in the past.

940
00:59:34,321 --> 00:59:35,655
And I was

941
00:59:35,739 --> 00:59:37,324
one of the bystanders

942
