who turned a blind eye to that violence.

943
00:59:41,203 --> 00:59:43,121
What do you mean?

944
00:59:43,747 --> 00:59:45,040
I'd like to submit as evidence

945
00:59:45,123 --> 00:59:47,042
a video recording from 12 years ago

946
00:59:47,125 --> 00:59:49,294
showing the defendant
being subjected to school violence.

947
