Your Honor, the source
of the video in question is unclear,

948
00:59:51,963 --> 00:59:54,466
and it has no direct relevance
to the current case.

949
00:59:54,549 --> 00:59:58,011
There's a high risk of further harm
to the victim and her family.

950
00:59:58,095 --> 00:59:59,096
That is correct.

951
00:59:59,888 --> 01:00:01,389
As the prosecution has stated,

952
01:00:01,473 --> 01:00:05,185
this video has no direct relevance
to the current case.

953
01:00:05,268 --> 01:00:06,478
However,

954
01:00:06,561 --> 01:00:09,689
this is a key piece of evidence
in determining the defendant's sentence

955
01:00:09,773 --> 01:00:12,359
because it demonstrates
how the defendant's suffering

956
01:00:12,442 --> 01:00:15,320
from school bullying
has impacted her current mental state

957
01:00:15,403 --> 01:00:18,406
and contributed to the offense.

958
01:00:19,407 --> 01:00:23,578
If the evidence is submitted
to assist the defendant's sentencing,

959
01:00:24,746 --> 01:00:26,790
it may be admissible on a limited basis.

960
01:00:27,332 --> 01:00:29,084
I'll allow it.

961
01:00:30,127 --> 01:00:31,169
What?

962
01:00:31,253 --> 01:00:32,963
My daughter's dead.

963
01:00:33,672 --> 01:00:35,423
And you want to show
a bullying video now?

964
01:00:35,507 --> 01:00:38,218
Who cares about
stupid school violence videos!

965
01:00:39,427 --> 01:00:41,304
Order in my court!

966
01:00:41,388 --> 01:00:43,473
Do you seriously call yourself a judge?

967
01:00:45,392 --> 01:00:46,518
Why?

968
01:00:47,310 --> 01:00:50,105
Why are you defending the murderer?

969
01:00:50,188 --> 01:00:51,398
Bailiff, escort her out.

970
01:00:52,023 --> 01:00:53,150
Get off me!

971
01:00:53,233 --> 01:00:55,152
Get off me!

972
01:00:55,235 --> 01:00:56,987
Let go of me!

973
01:00:57,070 --> 01:00:58,697
I won't let you get away with this!

974
01:00:58,780 --> 01:01:00,782
I swear I'll kill you all!

975
01:01:01,449 --> 01:01:03,368
Counsel, you may proceed.

976
01:01:04,870 --> 01:01:06,246
Your Honor,

977
01:01:06,329 --> 01:01:08,331
before the video is played,

978
01:01:08,415 --> 01:01:10,834
may the defendant be permitted
to wear an eye mask

979
01:01:10,917 --> 01:01:13,837
and noise-canceling headphones
during the screening

980
01:01:13,920 --> 01:01:16,464
to minimize potential distress
from trauma?

981
01:01:17,090 --> 01:01:18,717
I'll allow it.

982
01:01:22,470 --> 01:01:25,432
Would you like to cover your eyes
and listen to the music?

983
01:01:26,433 --> 01:01:27,642
Mr. Yoon.

