01:03:19,754 --> 01:03:21,506
The defendant, Kim Yeong-mi,

997
01:03:22,132 --> 01:03:24,009
was a bright and diligent student

998
01:03:24,092 --> 01:03:25,802
who consistently ranked first
in her school

999
01:03:25,885 --> 01:03:28,888
throughout middle school
and her first year of high school.

1000
01:03:28,972 --> 01:03:31,808
