who laughed with her friends

1001
01:03:31,891 --> 01:03:35,562
<i>and dreamed of the future.</i>

1002
01:03:37,605 --> 01:03:41,067
<i>Had it not been</i>
<i>for the cruel bullying she endured,</i>

1003
01:03:41,151 --> 01:03:44,237
<i>she wouldn't be standing here today</i>
<i>as a defendant</i>

1004
01:03:45,822 --> 01:03:47,324
and instead be out in the world

1005
01:03:47,407 --> 01:03:50,535
contributing to society
and realizing her full potential.

1006
01:03:51,953 --> 01:03:54,414
